A HDFS plugin for Xrootd.

This package is maintained by CMS.  The spec file is included upstream;
any changes you make here should also be placed in upstream Github:

https://github.com/bbockelm/xrootd-hdfs

Spec file obtained from spec/xrootd-hdfs.spec inside the repo.

To get the upstream:

git clone https://github.com/bbockelm/xrootd-hdfs.git
cd xrootd-hdfs
git archive v1.8.6 | gzip -7 > xrootd-hdfs.tar.gz

Or just do:

git clone https://github.com/bbockelm/xrootd-hdfs.git
cd xrootd-hdfs
git archive v1.8.8 --format=tar.gz --prefix=xrootd-hdfs-1.8.8/ -o ~/xrootd-hdfs-1.8.8.tar.gz -9
